---- termachat help page ----

@list
    List all existing chatrooms

@create <chatroom_name>
    Create chatroom named chatroom_name

@join <chatroom_name>
    Join chatroom named chatroom_name

@leave
    Leave the chatroom

@delete <chatroom_name>
    Deletes chatroom named chatroom_name

@current
    Get notified of which chatroom you're in currently

@w <text>
    Write text to your current chatroom

@r
    Read from your current chatroom

@pm <user_name>
    Private messages user named user_name

@exit
    End the subprocess and exit the client program

@help
    Display this page